cast.name: 爱丽丝·罗伯茨 Alice Roberts
斯蒂芙·麦戈文 Steph McGovern

introduction: Sue Perkins presents this brand new comedy panel show, Insert Name Here, all about famous people, past and present, who have just one thing in common: they share the same name.Each episode centres around one chosen name. Our entertaining host invites the two teams, headed up by captains Richard Osman and Josh Widdicombe, to battle it out, answering questions and competing to earn the right at the end of the game to decide the greatest ever bearer of that episode’s name.
